CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FOfficers were alerted by CCTV
OL,7,Foperators to the 23-year-old walking
OL,8,Falong Week Street inhaling gas-filled
OL,9,Fballoons. A search found inside his
OL,10,Fbumbag, there was a large amount of
OL,11,Fsmall bags filled with yellow tablets,
OL,12,Fwhite powder, and #240 in cash.
OL,14,FA search at Bryn's home address in
OL,15,FChurch Road in Eastchurch found
OL,16,Fthousands of pounds in cash along with
OL,17,Flarge quantities of ketamine, MDMA and
OL,18,Famphetamine.
OL,20,FMachinery used for producing pills was
OL,21,Ffound in the garage and seized.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FBryn was bailed while detectives
OL,7,Freviewed the messages on his mobile
OL,8,Fphone.
OL,10,FPolice say it showed that not only was
OL,11,Fhe selling drugs, but together with
OL,12,Fhis 27-year-old brother Connor Graham,
OL,13,Fwas involved in a large-scale
OL,14,Fproduction and supply of class A and B
OL,15,Fdrugs themselves.
OL,17,FAt the time, Connor Graham was already
OL,18,Fserving a prison sentence for similar
OL,19,Foffences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
