OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FOn Sunday 14 December 2025, both
OL,7,Fbrothers were arrested and another
OL,8,Fsearch was carried out at their home
OL,9,Faddress, where police found more
OL,10,Findustrial equipment had been
OL,11,Finstalled and set up to make pills,
OL,12,Fand a big selection of drugs ready for
OL,13,Fsale.
OL,15,FOfficers seized the equipment and two
OL,16,Fkilograms of MDMA, around 5,000
OL,17,Fecstasy pills, cocaine and #1,800 in
OL,18,Fcash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FThe two brothers were charged with
OL,7,Fproduction of MDMA, being concerned in
OL,8,Fthe supply of ketamine and
OL,9,Famphetamine, and possession of
OL,10,Fcriminal property. Bryn was also
OL,11,Fcharged with possession of cocaine.
OL,13,FAt Maidstone Crown Court they admitted
OL,14,Fthe charges. Bryn Graham did not enter
OL,15,Fa plea for possession of criminal
OL,16,Fproperty, and it was agreed that the
OL,17,Fcharge would remain on his file.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FThe two men also admitted breaching
OL,7,Fsuspended sentence orders, which
OL,8,Fpolice say were then activated and
OL,9,Fincorporated into their sentences on
OL,10,FThursday 26 February 2026.
OL,12,FBryn Graham received a seven-year
OL,13,Fsentence, and Connor Graham, who was
OL,14,Fseen as playing a bigger part in the
OL,15,Foffending, was sentenced to nine years
OL,16,Fand three months imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,7,FConstable Steve Brown said: "This was
OL,8,Fa significant sentence for two men who
OL,9,Fwere instrumental in an industrial-
OL,10,Fsized pill production enterprise.
OL,12,F"They produced large amounts of
OL,13,Fecstasy and ketamine. The sheer number
OL,14,Fof pills ready for sale seized by
OL,15,Fofficers illustrated just how far-
OL,16,Freaching their production line was
OL,17,Fintending to be, and how many lives
OL,18,Fcould have been ruined, had the pills
OL,19,Fmade it out for sale.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
