OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772791513
OL,3,CBrothers jailed after police discover
OL,4,Clarge-scale ecstasy operation
OL,6,F"As well as custodial sentences, the
OL,7,FGraham brothers will now be subject to
OL,8,Fa hearing under the Proceeds of Crime
OL,9,Fact to confiscate their earnings and
OL,10,Fensure they do not profit from their
OL,11,Fcriminal endeavours."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
